<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <style>
        .text {
            float: left;
            width: 50%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding-top: 100px;
            padding-left: 30px;
        }

        .pic {
            float: right;
            width: 50%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding-top: 90px;
        }

        .pic img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .button-container {
            padding-left: 40px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 260px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .clearfix::after {
            content: "";
            display: table;
            clear: both;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border: 1px solid #007bff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            border-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="clearfix">
        <div class="text">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom:40px;">This Week's Activity</h2>
            <h1 style="color: dodgerblue; font-size: 66px; margin-bottom:40px;">Water Waste</h1>
            <p>Water Waste is not just about leaving the tap on for too long - Let's dive in and learn how saving water can help save our planet</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <h2 style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';">Watch & Learn <img src="~/Media/LearnVideo.png" style="width:60px;height:auto;" /></h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pic">
            <img src="~/Media/WelcomePage.png" alt="Placeholder Image">

            <video width="640" height="360" controls>
                <source src="@ViewBag.VideoUrl" type="video/mp4">
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

